{"tid":1835021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護手足請入","createTime":"2020-01-22T16:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T17:21:21.000Z","uid":252031,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b4bc2827479c99dcf1f0af3d0a5f1a16be8c85cc","tid":1835021,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:08:08.000Z","msg":"呢個係我地逼迫政府回應五大訴求嘅好時機，趁我地仲有bargaining power，我地要求政府公開回應五大訴求同邊境出入口管制，否則發起罷工<br />\n<br />\n支持，政府一路漠視民意，年年唔夠人手鄭係識叫我地前線醫護挨義氣頂硬上仲cut budget，popo姦淫虜掠就有10億Ot錢，再忍氣吞聲落去就係縱容呢個政權打壓我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對，醫護罷工有道德壓力，呢d時候應該共度時艱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2813b83555491536900ea619bb78bb432f47a58","tid":1835021,"uid":252031,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"我贊成各工會儘快達成罷工共識，一齊罷佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位手足口做好安全防疫措施<br />\n等藍絲物競天擇"},{"pid":"e009ae0452d3769067100d5b93834e26448debc2","tid":1835021,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4191f577df300e714ec6081b81c3f725ae8cf3","tid":1835021,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:10:09.000Z","msg":"時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e998846f2443be813255c1bee71f3b237c6c501","tid":1835021,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74fc6a578509bc9c3c7d37f786fe38a38a84938","tid":1835021,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:10:32.000Z","msg":"缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/